{
  "video_id": "gzthxdm7XNs",
  "title": "Todd Humphreys: How to fool a GPS",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 13527.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 13527.0,
      "end_time": 16315.0,
      "text": "Something happened in the early morning hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16315.000000000002,
      "end_time": 19900.0,
      "text": "of May 2nd, 2000, that had a profound effect"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19900.0,
      "end_time": 22206.0,
      "text": "on the way our society operates."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22206.0,
      "end_time": 25484.0,
      "text": "Ironically, hardly anyone noticed at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25484.0,
      "end_time": 28144.0,
      "text": "The change was silent, imperceptible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28144.0,
      "end_time": 30989.0,
      "text": "unless you knew exactly what to look for."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30989.0,
      "end_time": 33340.0,
      "text": "On that morning, U.S. President Bill Clinton"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33340.0,
      "end_time": 35612.0,
      "text": "ordered that a special switch be thrown"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35612.0,
      "end_time": 39045.0,
      "text": "in the orbiting satellites of the Global Positioning System."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39045.0,
      "end_time": 42909.0,
      "text": "Instantaneously, every civilian GPS receiver"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42909.0,
      "end_time": 47471.0,
      "text": "around the globe went from errors the size of a football field"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47471.0,
      "end_time": 54314.0,
      "text": "to errors the size of a small room."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54314.0,
      "end_time": 58105.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hard to overstate the effect that this change"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 58105.0,
      "end_time": 60657.0,
      "text": "in accuracy has had on us."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 60657.0,
      "end_time": 62904.0,
      "text": "Before this switch was thrown, we didn&#39;t have"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 62904.0,
      "end_time": 65163.0,
      "text": "in-car navigation systems giving turn-by-turn"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65163.0,
      "end_time": 67755.0,
      "text": "directions, because back then, GPS couldn&#39;t tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67755.0,
      "end_time": 70449.0,
      "text": "what block you were on, let alone what street."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70449.0,
      "end_time": 73697.0,
      "text": "For geolocation, accuracy matters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 73697.0,
      "end_time": 76955.0,
      "text": "and things have only improved over the last 10 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 76955.0,
      "end_time": 79074.0,
      "text": "With more base stations, more ground stations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79074.0,
      "end_time": 82043.0,
      "text": "better receivers and better algorithms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82043.0,
      "end_time": 85106.0,
      "text": "GPS can now not only tell you what street you are on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85106.0,
      "end_time": 89608.0,
      "text": "but what part of the street."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 89608.0,
      "end_time": 91854.0,
      "text": "This level of accuracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 91854.0,
      "end_time": 94780.0,
      "text": "has unleashed a firestorm of innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94780.0,
      "end_time": 97451.0,
      "text": "In fact, many of you navigated here today"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 97451.0,
      "end_time": 101044.0,
      "text": "with the help of your TomTom or your smartphone."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101044.0,
      "end_time": 104269.0,
      "text": "Paper maps are becoming obsolete."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 104269.0,
      "end_time": 108408.0,
      "text": "But we now stand on the verge of another revolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 108408.0,
      "end_time": 110403.0,
      "text": "in geolocation accuracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 110403.0,
      "end_time": 113136.0,
      "text": "What if I told you that the two-meter positioning"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 113136.0,
      "end_time": 116567.0,
      "text": "that our current cell phones and our TomToms give us"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 116567.0,
      "end_time": 120464.0,
      "text": "is pathetic compared to what we could be getting?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 120464.0,
      "end_time": 123297.0,
      "text": "For some time now, it&#39;s been known that if you pay attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 123297.0,
      "end_time": 125832.0,
      "text": "to the carrier phase of the GPS signal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125832.0,
      "end_time": 128313.0,
      "text": "and if you have an Internet connection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 128312.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131129.0,
      "text": "then you can go from meter level to centimeter level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131129.0,
      "end_time": 134096.0,
      "text": "even millimeter-level positioning."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 134096.0,
      "end_time": 137376.0,
      "text": "So why don&#39;t we have this capability on our phones?"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 137376.0,
      "end_time": 141746.0,
      "text": "Only, I believe, for a lack of imagination."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 141746.0,
      "end_time": 144913.0,
      "text": "Manufacturers haven&#39;t built this carrier phase technique"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 144913.0,
      "end_time": 147019.0,
      "text": "into their cheap GPS chips"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 147019.0,
      "end_time": 149173.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re not sure what the general public would do"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 149173.0,
      "end_time": 152749.0,
      "text": "with geolocation so accurate that you could pinpoint"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 152749.0,
      "end_time": 156587.0,
      "text": "the wrinkles in the palm of your hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 156587.0,
      "end_time": 158974.0,
      "text": "But you and I and other innovators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 158974.0,
      "end_time": 163014.0,
      "text": "we can see the potential in this next leap in accuracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 163014.0,
      "end_time": 165726.0,
      "text": "Imagine, for example, an augmented reality app"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 165726.0,
      "end_time": 169263.0,
      "text": "that overlays a virtual world to millimeter-level precision"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 169263.0,
      "end_time": 171271.0,
      "text": "on top of the physical world."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 171271.0,
      "end_time": 174158.0,
      "text": "I could build for you a structure up here in 3D,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 174158.0,
      "end_time": 176526.0,
      "text": "millimeter accurate, that only you could see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 176526.0,
      "end_time": 179419.0,
      "text": "or my friends at home."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 179419.0,
      "end_time": 183934.0,
      "text": "So this level of positioning, this is what we&#39;re looking for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 183934.0,
      "end_time": 187858.0,
      "text": "and I believe that, within the next few years, I predict,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 187858.0,
      "end_time": 192841.0,
      "text": "that this kind of hyper-precise, carrier phase-based positioning"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 192841.0,
      "end_time": 196065.0,
      "text": "will become cheap and ubiquitous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 196065.0,
      "end_time": 198610.0,
      "text": "and the consequences will be fantastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 198610.0,
      "end_time": 203266.0,
      "text": "The Holy Grail, of course, is the GPS dot."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 203266.0,
      "end_time": 205946.0,
      "text": "Do you remember the movie &quot;The Da Vinci Code?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 205946.0,
      "end_time": 209394.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s Professor Langdon examining a GPS dot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 209394.0,
      "end_time": 212771.0,
      "text": "which his accomplice tells him is a tracking device"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 212771.0,
      "end_time": 215832.0,
      "text": "accurate within two feet anywhere on the globe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 215832.0,
      "end_time": 218738.0,
      "text": "but we know that in the world of nonfiction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 218738.0,
      "end_time": 221602.0,
      "text": "the GPS dot is impossible, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 221602.0,
      "end_time": 224226.0,
      "text": "For one thing, GPS doesn&#39;t work indoors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 224226.0,
      "end_time": 227410.0,
      "text": "and for another, they don&#39;t make devices quite this small,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 227410.0,
      "end_time": 229738.0,
      "text": "especially when those devices have to relay"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 229738.0,
      "end_time": 232713.0,
      "text": "their measurements back over a network."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 232713.0,
      "end_time": 235051.0,
      "text": "Well, these objections were perfectly reasonable"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 235051.0,
      "end_time": 238065.0,
      "text": "a few years ago, but things have changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 238065.0,
      "end_time": 240921.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s been a strong trend toward miniaturization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 240921.0,
      "end_time": 244640.0,
      "text": "better sensitivity, so much so that, a few years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 244640.0,
      "end_time": 247344.0,
      "text": "a GPS tracking device looked like this clunky box"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 247344.0,
      "end_time": 249520.0,
      "text": "to the left of the keys."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 249520.0,
      "end_time": 252171.0,
      "text": "Compare that with the device released just months ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 252171.0,
      "end_time": 255963.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s now packaged into something the size of a key fob,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 255963.0,
      "end_time": 258516.0,
      "text": "and if you take a look at the state of the art"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 258516.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261262.00000000003,
      "text": "for a complete GPS receiver, which is only a centimeter"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 261262.0,
      "end_time": 263349.0,
      "text": "on a side and more sensitive than ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 263349.0,
      "end_time": 266858.0,
      "text": "you realize that the GPS dot will soon move"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 266858.0,
      "end_time": 271257.0,
      "text": "from fiction to nonfiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 271257.0,
      "end_time": 275499.0,
      "text": "Imagine what we could do with a world full of GPS dots."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 275499.0,
      "end_time": 278405.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not just that you&#39;ll never lose your wallet or your keys"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 278405.0,
      "end_time": 282976.0,
      "text": "anymore, or your child when you&#39;re at Disneyland."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 282976.0,
      "end_time": 286757.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll buy GPS dots in bulk, and you&#39;ll stick them on"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 286757.0,
      "end_time": 290724.0,
      "text": "everything you own worth more than a few tens of dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 290724.0,
      "end_time": 293196.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t find my shoes one recent morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 293196.0,
      "end_time": 296564.0,
      "text": "and, as usual, had to ask my wife if she had seen them."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 296564.0,
      "end_time": 300356.0,
      "text": "But I shouldn&#39;t have to bother my wife with that kind of triviality."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 300356.0,
      "end_time": 302967.0,
      "text": "I should be able to ask my house where my shoes are."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 302967.0,
      "end_time": 305106.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 305106.0,
      "end_time": 308614.0,
      "text": "Those of you who have made the switch to Gmail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 308614.0,
      "end_time": 311492.0,
      "text": "remember how refreshing it was to go from"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 311492.0,
      "end_time": 315636.0,
      "text": "organizing all of your email to simply searching it."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 315636.0,
      "end_time": 320138.0,
      "text": "The GPS dot will do the same for our possessions."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 320138.0,
      "end_time": 324824.0,
      "text": "Now, of course, there is a flip side to the GPS dot."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 324824.0,
      "end_time": 327213.0,
      "text": "I was in my office some months back"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 327213.0,
      "end_time": 329756.0,
      "text": "and got a telephone call."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 329756.0,
      "end_time": 333377.0,
      "text": "The woman on the other end of the line, we&#39;ll call her Carol,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 333377.0,
      "end_time": 335456.0,
      "text": "was panicked."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 335456.0,
      "end_time": 338249.0,
      "text": "Apparently, an ex-boyfriend of Carol&#39;s from California"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 338249.0,
      "end_time": 341564.0,
      "text": "had found her in Texas and was following her around."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 341564.0,
      "end_time": 345401.0,
      "text": "So you might ask at this point why she&#39;s calling you."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 345401.0,
      "end_time": 346800.0,
      "text": "Well, so did I."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 346800.0,
      "end_time": 350791.0,
      "text": "But it turned out there was a technical twist to Carol&#39;s case."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 350791.0,
      "end_time": 353525.0,
      "text": "Every time her ex-boyfriend would show up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 353525.0,
      "end_time": 357875.0,
      "text": "at the most improbable times and the most improbable locations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 357875.0,
      "end_time": 360571.0,
      "text": "he was carrying an open laptop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 360571.0,
      "end_time": 363414.0,
      "text": "and over time Carol realized that he had planted"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 363414.0,
      "end_time": 365962.0,
      "text": "a GPS tracking device on her car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 365962.0,
      "end_time": 368871.0,
      "text": "so she was calling me for help to disable it."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 368871.0,
      "end_time": 370859.0,
      "text": "&quot;Well, you should go to a good mechanic"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 370859.0,
      "end_time": 374143.0,
      "text": "and have him look at your car,&quot; I said."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 374143.0,
      "end_time": 376847.0,
      "text": "&quot;I already have,&quot; she told me."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 376847.0,
      "end_time": 378991.0,
      "text": "&quot;He didn&#39;t see anything obvious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 378991.0,
      "end_time": 382528.0,
      "text": "and he said he&#39;d have to take the car apart piece by piece.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 382528.0,
      "end_time": 385849.0,
      "text": "&quot;Well then, you&#39;d better go to the police,&quot; I said."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 385849.0,
      "end_time": 388953.0,
      "text": "&quot;I already have,&quot; she replied."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 388953.0,
      "end_time": 391399.0,
      "text": "&quot;They&#39;re not sure this rises to the level of harassment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 391399.0,
      "end_time": 395152.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re not set up technically to find the device.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 395152.0,
      "end_time": 396658.0,
      "text": "&quot;Okay, what about the FBI?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 396658.0,
      "end_time": 400821.0,
      "text": "&quot;I&#39;ve talked to them too, and same story.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 400821.0,
      "end_time": 402491.0,
      "text": "We then talked about her coming to my lab"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 402491.0,
      "end_time": 405039.0,
      "text": "and us performing a radio sweep of her car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 405039.0,
      "end_time": 407538.0,
      "text": "but I wasn&#39;t even sure that would work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 407538.0,
      "end_time": 409589.0,
      "text": "given that some of these devices are configured"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 409589.0,
      "end_time": 411823.0,
      "text": "to only transmit when they&#39;re inside safe zones"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 411823.0,
      "end_time": 415127.0,
      "text": "or when the car is moving."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 415127.0,
      "end_time": 416621.0,
      "text": "So, there we were."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 416621.0,
      "end_time": 419590.0,
      "text": "Carol isn&#39;t the first, and certainly won&#39;t be the last,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 419590.0,
      "end_time": 424525.0,
      "text": "to find herself in this kind of fearsome environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 424525.0,
      "end_time": 430410.0,
      "text": "worrisome situation caused by GPS tracking."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 430410.0,
      "end_time": 432213.0,
      "text": "In fact, as I looked into her case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 432213.0,
      "end_time": 435675.0,
      "text": "I discovered to my surprise that it&#39;s not clearly illegal"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 435675.0,
      "end_time": 440108.0,
      "text": "for you or me to put a tracking device on someone else&#39;s car."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 440108.0,
      "end_time": 443988.0,
      "text": "The Supreme Court ruled last month that a policeman"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 443988.0,
      "end_time": 448320.0,
      "text": "has to get a warrant if he wants to do prolonged tracking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 448320.0,
      "end_time": 451836.0,
      "text": "but the law isn&#39;t clear about civilians doing this to one another,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 451836.0,
      "end_time": 454466.0,
      "text": "so it&#39;s not just Big Brother we have to worry about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 454466.0,
      "end_time": 457737.0,
      "text": "but Big Neighbor. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 457737.0,
      "end_time": 462385.0,
      "text": "There is one alternative that Carol could have taken,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 462385.0,
      "end_time": 468088.0,
      "text": "very effective. It&#39;s called the Wave Bubble."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 468088.0,
      "end_time": 471023.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an open-source GPS jammer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 471023.0,
      "end_time": 473578.0,
      "text": "developed by Limor Fried,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 473578.0,
      "end_time": 477371.0,
      "text": "a graduate student at MIT, and Limor calls it"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 477371.0,
      "end_time": 481256.0,
      "text": "&quot;a tool for reclaiming our personal space.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 481256.0,
      "end_time": 483521.0,
      "text": "With a flip of the switch you create a bubble around you"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 483521.0,
      "end_time": 485768.0,
      "text": "within which GPS signals can&#39;t reside."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 485768.0,
      "end_time": 488124.0,
      "text": "They get drowned out by the bubble."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 488124.0,
      "end_time": 491771.0,
      "text": "And Limor designed this, in part, because, like Carol,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 491771.0,
      "end_time": 494417.0,
      "text": "she felt threatened by GPS tracking."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 494417.0,
      "end_time": 496993.0,
      "text": "Then she posted her design to the web,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 496993.0,
      "end_time": 500735.0,
      "text": "and if you don&#39;t have time to build your own,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 500735.0,
      "end_time": 501509.0,
      "text": "you can buy one."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 501509.0,
      "end_time": 503567.0,
      "text": "Chinese manufacturers now sell thousands"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 503567.0,
      "end_time": 507340.0,
      "text": "of nearly identical devices on the Internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 507340.0,
      "end_time": 511492.0,
      "text": "So you might be thinking, the Wave Bubble sounds great."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 511492.0,
      "end_time": 515145.0,
      "text": "I should have one. Might come in handy if somebody ever puts a tracking device on my car."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 515145.0,
      "end_time": 518927.0,
      "text": "But you should be aware that its use is very much illegal"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 518927.0,
      "end_time": 520726.0,
      "text": "in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 520726.0,
      "end_time": 521473.0,
      "text": "And why is that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 521472.99999999994,
      "end_time": 524566.0,
      "text": "Well, because it&#39;s not a bubble at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 524566.0,
      "end_time": 526965.0,
      "text": "Its jamming signals don&#39;t stop at the edge"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 526965.0,
      "end_time": 529437.0,
      "text": "of your personal space or at the edge of your car."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 529437.0,
      "end_time": 535673.0,
      "text": "They go on to jam innocent GPS receivers for miles around you. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 535673.0,
      "end_time": 538424.0,
      "text": "Now, if you&#39;re Carol or Limor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 538424.0,
      "end_time": 541049.0,
      "text": "or someone who feels threatened by GPS tracking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 541049.0,
      "end_time": 544824.0,
      "text": "it might not feel wrong to turn on a Wave Bubble,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 544824.0,
      "end_time": 548804.0,
      "text": "but in fact, the results can be disastrous."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 548804.0,
      "end_time": 551524.0,
      "text": "Imagine, for example, you&#39;re the captain of a cruise ship"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 551524.0,
      "end_time": 554043.0,
      "text": "trying to make your way through a thick fog"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 554043.0,
      "end_time": 557883.0,
      "text": "and some passenger in the back turns on a Wave Bubble."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 557883.0,
      "end_time": 560598.0,
      "text": "All of a sudden your GPS readout goes blank,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 560598.0,
      "end_time": 563884.0,
      "text": "and now it&#39;s just you and the fog"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 563884.0,
      "end_time": 566484.0,
      "text": "and whatever you can pull off the radar system"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 566484.0,
      "end_time": 569608.0,
      "text": "if you remember how to work it."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 569608.0,
      "end_time": 575544.0,
      "text": "They -- in fact, they don&#39;t update or upkeep lighthouses"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 575544.0,
      "end_time": 580197.0,
      "text": "anymore, and LORAN, the only backup to GPS,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 580197.0,
      "end_time": 582617.0,
      "text": "was discontinued last year."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 582617.0,
      "end_time": 587530.0,
      "text": "Our modern society has a special relationship with GPS."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 587530.0,
      "end_time": 589800.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re almost blindly reliant on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 589800.0,
      "end_time": 593451.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s built deeply into our systems and infrastructure."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 593451.0,
      "end_time": 597079.0,
      "text": "Some call it &quot;the invisible utility.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 597079.0,
      "end_time": 600801.0,
      "text": "So, turning on a Wave Bubble might not just cause inconvenience."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 600801.0,
      "end_time": 605171.0,
      "text": "It might be deadly."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 605171.0,
      "end_time": 609379.0,
      "text": "But as it turns out, for purposes of protecting your privacy"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 609379.0,
      "end_time": 612868.0,
      "text": "at the expense of general GPS reliability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 612868.0,
      "end_time": 615028.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s something even more potent"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 615028.0,
      "end_time": 618820.0,
      "text": "and more subversive than a Wave Bubble,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 618820.0,
      "end_time": 622209.0,
      "text": "and that is a GPS spoofer."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 622209.0,
      "end_time": 625034.0,
      "text": "The idea behind the GPS spoofer is simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 625034.0,
      "end_time": 629011.0,
      "text": "Instead of jamming the GPS signals, you fake them."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 629011.0,
      "end_time": 632129.0,
      "text": "You imitate them, and if you do it right, the device"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 632129.0,
      "end_time": 635296.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re attacking doesn&#39;t even know it&#39;s being spoofed."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 635296.0,
      "end_time": 636928.0,
      "text": "So let me show you how this works."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 636928.0,
      "end_time": 639653.0,
      "text": "In any GPS receiver, there&#39;s a peak inside"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 639653.0,
      "end_time": 642288.0,
      "text": "that corresponds to the authentic signals."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 642288.0,
      "end_time": 645103.0,
      "text": "These three red dots represent the tracking points"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 645103.0,
      "end_time": 647982.0,
      "text": "that try to keep themselves centered on that peak."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 647982.0,
      "end_time": 651047.0,
      "text": "But if you send in a fake GPS signal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 651047.0,
      "end_time": 655513.0,
      "text": "another peak pops up, and if you can get these two peaks"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 655513.0,
      "end_time": 660231.0,
      "text": "perfectly aligned, the tracking points can&#39;t tell the difference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 660231.0,
      "end_time": 663542.0,
      "text": "and they get hijacked by the stronger counterfeit signal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 663542.0,
      "end_time": 667502.0,
      "text": "with the authentic peak getting forced off."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 667502.0,
      "end_time": 669669.0,
      "text": "At this point, the game is over."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 669669.0,
      "end_time": 673406.0,
      "text": "The fake signals now completely control this GPS receiver."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 673406.0,
      "end_time": 674901.0,
      "text": "So is this really possible?"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 674901.0,
      "end_time": 676624.0,
      "text": "Can someone really manipulate"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 676624.0,
      "end_time": 678606.0,
      "text": "the timing and positioning of a GPS receiver"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 678606.0,
      "end_time": 681485.0,
      "text": "just like that, with a spoofer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 681485.0,
      "end_time": 683500.0,
      "text": "Well, the short answer is yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 683500.0,
      "end_time": 686304.0,
      "text": "The key is that civil GPS signals"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 686304.0,
      "end_time": 687406.0,
      "text": "are completely open."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 687406.0,
      "end_time": 691397.0,
      "text": "They have no encryption. They have no authentication."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 691397.0,
      "end_time": 694892.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re wide open, vulnerable to a kind of spoofing attack."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 694892.0,
      "end_time": 697467.0,
      "text": "Even so, up until very recently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 697467.0,
      "end_time": 699859.0,
      "text": "nobody worried about GPS spoofers."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 699859.0,
      "end_time": 701837.0,
      "text": "People figured that it would be too complex"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 701837.0,
      "end_time": 704652.0,
      "text": "or too expensive for some hacker to build one."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 704652.0,
      "end_time": 708604.0,
      "text": "But I, and a friend of mine from graduate school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 708604.0,
      "end_time": 710756.0,
      "text": "we didn&#39;t see it that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 710756.0,
      "end_time": 713229.0,
      "text": "We knew it wasn&#39;t going to be so hard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 713229.0,
      "end_time": 715157.0,
      "text": "and we wanted to be the first to build one"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 715157.0,
      "end_time": 717237.0,
      "text": "so we could get out in front of the problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 717237.0,
      "end_time": 721343.0,
      "text": "and help protect against GPS spoofing."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 721343.0,
      "end_time": 724688.0,
      "text": "I remember vividly the week it all came together."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 724688.0,
      "end_time": 728137.0,
      "text": "We built it at my home, which means that"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 728137.0,
      "end_time": 732526.0,
      "text": "I got a little extra help from my three-year-old son Ramon."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 732526.0,
      "end_time": 734944.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s Ramon — (Laughter) —"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 734944.0,
      "end_time": 738629.0,
      "text": "looking for a little attention from Dad that week."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 738629.0,
      "end_time": 740899.0,
      "text": "At first, the spoofer was just a jumble of cables"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 740899.0,
      "end_time": 743781.0,
      "text": "and computers, though we eventually got it packaged"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 743781.0,
      "end_time": 745453.0,
      "text": "into a small box."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 745453.0,
      "end_time": 748262.0,
      "text": "Now, the Dr. Frankenstein moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 748262.0,
      "end_time": 750989.0,
      "text": "when the spoofer finally came alive"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 750989.0,
      "end_time": 753590.0,
      "text": "and I glimpsed its awful potential,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 753590.0,
      "end_time": 756326.0,
      "text": "came late one night when I tested the spoofer"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 756326.0,
      "end_time": 758412.0,
      "text": "against my iPhone."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 758412.0,
      "end_time": 760029.0,
      "text": "Let me show you some actual footage from that"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 760029.0,
      "end_time": 761965.0,
      "text": "very first experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 761965.0,
      "end_time": 765559.0,
      "text": "I had come to completely trust this little blue dot"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 765559.0,
      "end_time": 767194.0,
      "text": "and its reassuring blue halo."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 767194.0,
      "end_time": 768269.0,
      "text": "They seemed to speak to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 768269.0,
      "end_time": 772929.0,
      "text": "They&#39;d say, &quot;Here you are. Here you are.&quot; (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 772929.0,
      "end_time": 775799.0,
      "text": "And &quot;you can trust us.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 775799.0,
      "end_time": 780917.0,
      "text": "So something felt very wrong about the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 780917.0,
      "end_time": 783500.0,
      "text": "It was a sense, almost, of betrayal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 783500.0,
      "end_time": 787691.0,
      "text": "when this little blue dot started at my house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 787691.0,
      "end_time": 789303.0,
      "text": "and went running off toward the north"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 789303.0,
      "end_time": 793198.0,
      "text": "leaving me behind. I wasn&#39;t moving."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 793198.0,
      "end_time": 797431.0,
      "text": "What I then saw in this little moving blue dot"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 797431.0,
      "end_time": 800149.0,
      "text": "was the potential for chaos."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 800149.0,
      "end_time": 804291.0,
      "text": "I saw airplanes and ships veering off course, with the captain"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 804291.0,
      "end_time": 808565.0,
      "text": "learning only too late that something was wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 808565.0,
      "end_time": 811065.0,
      "text": "I saw the GPS-derived timing"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 811065.0,
      "end_time": 812796.0,
      "text": "of the New York Stock Exchange"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 812796.0,
      "end_time": 814746.0,
      "text": "being manipulated by hackers."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 814746.0,
      "end_time": 817714.0,
      "text": "You can scarcely imagine the kind of havoc"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 817714.0,
      "end_time": 820364.0,
      "text": "you could cause if you knew what you were doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 820364.0,
      "end_time": 823717.0,
      "text": "with a GPS spoofer."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 823717.0,
      "end_time": 828861.0,
      "text": "There is, though, one redeeming feature"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 828861.0,
      "end_time": 831317.0,
      "text": "of the GPS spoofer."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 831317.0,
      "end_time": 835918.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the ultimate weapon against an invasion of GPS dots."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 835918.0,
      "end_time": 839005.0,
      "text": "Imagine, for example, you&#39;re being tracked."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 839005.0,
      "end_time": 841529.0,
      "text": "Well, you can play the tracker for a fool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 841529.0,
      "end_time": 844490.0,
      "text": "pretending to be at work when you&#39;re really on vacation."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 844490.0,
      "end_time": 847205.0,
      "text": "Or, if you&#39;re Carol, you could lure your ex-boyfriend"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 847205.0,
      "end_time": 848522.0,
      "text": "into some empty parking lot"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 848522.0,
      "end_time": 850823.0,
      "text": "where the police are waiting for him."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 850823.0,
      "end_time": 856026.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m fascinated by this conflict, a looming conflict,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 856026.0,
      "end_time": 858691.0,
      "text": "between privacy on the one hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 858691.0,
      "end_time": 862890.0,
      "text": "and the need for a clean radio spectrum on the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 862890.0,
      "end_time": 865935.0,
      "text": "We simply cannot tolerate GPS jammers and spoofers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 865935.0,
      "end_time": 869671.0,
      "text": "and yet, given the lack of effective legal means"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 869671.0,
      "end_time": 873770.0,
      "text": "for protecting our privacy from the GPS dot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 873770.0,
      "end_time": 875642.0,
      "text": "can you really blame people for wanting to turn them on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 875642.0,
      "end_time": 878058.0,
      "text": "for wanting to use them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 878058.0,
      "end_time": 881111.0,
      "text": "I hold out hope that we&#39;ll be able to reconcile"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 881111.0,
      "end_time": 884297.0,
      "text": "this conflict with some sort of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 884297.0,
      "end_time": 889727.0,
      "text": "some yet uninvented technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 889727.0,
      "end_time": 892853.0,
      "text": "But meanwhile, grab some popcorn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 892853.0,
      "end_time": 894980.0,
      "text": "because things are going to get interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 894980.0,
      "end_time": 896320.0,
      "text": "Within the next few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 896320.0,
      "end_time": 900574.0,
      "text": "many of you will be the proud owner of a GPS dot."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 900574.0,
      "end_time": 902922.0,
      "text": "Maybe you&#39;ll have a whole bag full of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 902922.0,
      "end_time": 906374.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll never lose track of your things again."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 906374.0,
      "end_time": 910403.0,
      "text": "The GPS dot will fundamentally reorder your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 910403.0,
      "end_time": 913085.0,
      "text": "But will you be able to resist the temptation"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 913085.0,
      "end_time": 916077.0,
      "text": "to track your fellow man?"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 916077.0,
      "end_time": 917909.0,
      "text": "Or will you be able to resist the temptation"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 917909.0,
      "end_time": 921204.0,
      "text": "to turn on a GPS spoofer or a Wave Bubble"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 921204.0,
      "end_time": 923972.0,
      "text": "to protect your own privacy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 923972.0,
      "end_time": 927604.0,
      "text": "So, as usual, what we see just beyond the horizon"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 927604.0,
      "end_time": 930944.0,
      "text": "is full of promise and peril."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 930944.0,
      "end_time": 934132.0,
      "text": "It&#39;ll be fascinating to see how this all turns out."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 934132.0,
      "end_time": 944132.0,
      "text": "Thanks. (Applause)"
    }
  ]
}